description: The "Adolescent Unplanned Pregnancy in the Pacific" reports present findings from Chuuk State (Federated States of Micronesia), Tonga and Vanuatu from research designed to shed light on the experiences of adolescent girls and young women who face unplanned pregnancy and motherhood.
name: Adolescent Unplanned Pregnancy in the Pacific (Chuuk, Tonga and Vanuatu)
